  "text": "DT kills cells by inducing apoptotic cell death, [CITATION_1] which is characterized by nuclear fragmentation and condensation. At 8 hours following DT injection, these nuclear changes were observed in the intima and were associated with CD11c \u03e9 cell membrane blebbing (Online Figure IV) . There was no indication of inflammatory response following DT treatment. In fact, real-time RT-PCR revealed that steady-state mRNA levels of proinflammatory genes interleukin (IL)-6 and IL-1\u2424 decreased significantly in the LC of the arch 24 hours following DT treatment, but significant differences in transforming growth factor-\u2424 expression levels were not observed (Online Figure V) .",
